      "description": "Lists all active and completed background agents.\n* Shows the status of running, idle, completed, failed, and cancelled background agents.\n* Idle agents are waiting for messages — use write_agent to send them follow-ups.\n* Use this to discover agent_ids for use with read_agent or write_agent tools.\n* Set include_completed: false to only show running and idle agents.",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
